{"tid":714790,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"想開個Tg group比有抑鬱問題嘅人","createTime":"2018-06-24T02:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T09:15:27.000Z","uid":79927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e22b78cde1147105f3b6b7215a50bc98c3a3a22","tid":714790,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"本身已經比抑鬱問題困擾左好耐<br />\n其實同人傾計係有助抒緩自己嘅抑鬱問題<br />\n但依方面嘅問題我好少會同朋友家人講<br />\n一來唔想令人覺得我負能量<br />\n二來佢地未體驗過抑鬱嘅話，根本好難溝通到<br />\n所以想開個Group比同樣有抑鬱問題嘅人圍爐<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE3JCDHJh08C0VHq4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE3JCDHJh08C0VHq4g&d=HcadlA1bA2XoVPK3oCgCFC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4026b5f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE3JCDHJh08C0VHq4g</a><br />\n由於依家得我一個人<br />\n開唔到Group<br />\n有興趣一齊圍爐嘅人請先subscribe左個channel<br />\n到有一定人數之後我會開Group然後放個group條link上黎"},{"pid":"3c6111f6e06baf4542492a7077288c8a9ce570d1","tid":714790,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"support<br />\n個group可唔可以都一齊努力做返好自己<br />\n我成日有好多野做然後都因為抑鬱就唔想做 一日推一日 直到我連起身都唔起 離開間房/張床都懶<br />\n同埋提大家食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47006d2e8fe9461aed6fbe9e29138e3bed11d736","tid":714790,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:03:47.000Z","msg":"成班負能量加抑鬱一齊放負 不敢想像會點"},{"pid":"ea963ac91c621f99620d9c249537826638e693e4","tid":714790,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47006d2e8fe9461aed6fbe9e29138e3bed11d736","tid":714790,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:03:47.000Z","msg":"成班負能量加抑鬱一齊放負 不敢想像會點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"長洲東堤會好熱鬧"},{"pid":"d83b5ac60cbeb340fe9caa6635fcde35821d8b47","tid":714790,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6111f6e06baf4542492a7077288c8a9ce570d1","tid":714790,"uid":5098